Ifo’s Sinn Says No Alternative to Greek Euro Exit, Welt Reports

-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 
2011-09-14T18:07:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-14/ifo-s-sinn-says-no-alternative-to-greek-euro-exit-welt-reports.html
Hans-Werner Sinn, president of the
Munich-based Ifo Institute, said there is no alternative to
 Greece  leaving the euro area,  Die Welt  newspaper reported,
citing an interview.  Sinn said Greece could temporarily reintroduce the drachma
to improve the country’s competitiveness, the newspaper
reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeff Black in Frankfurt 
